OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781475073
OL,3,CFunding boost for after-school clubs
OL,4,Cahead of expected social media ban
OL,6,FThe government has announced a funding
OL,7,Fboost for after-school clubs ahead of
OL,8,Fan expected under-16s social media ban.
OL,10,FThe #132.5 million-backed programme
OL,11,Fwill fund activities to keep children
OL,12,Foccupied and help them build new
OL,13,Fskills, which could include music
OL,14,Fgroups, engineering clubs, debating
OL,15,Fsocieties and football clubs.
OL,17,FOfsted will consider a school's
OL,18,Fenrichment offer as part of how it
OL,19,Fassesses personal development, the
OL,20,FDepartment for Education said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781475073
OL,3,CFunding boost for after-school clubs
OL,4,Cahead of expected social media ban
OL,6,FMinisters hope the funding boost will
OL,7,Frespond directly to the State of the
OL,8,FNation survey of more than 14,000
OL,9,Fyoung people, which found that despite
OL,10,Fbeing the most digitally connected
OL,11,Fgeneration, young people today face
OL,12,Fsome of the highest levels of
OL,13,Fisolation.
OL,15,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer is
OL,16,Fwidely expected to introduce
OL,17,Frestrictions on children's social
OL,18,Fmedia use in the coming days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
