FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781475073
OL,3,CFunding boost for after-school clubs
OL,4,Cahead of expected social media ban
OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Liz Kendall has
OL,7,Fsaid an Australian-style ban is "on
OL,8,Fthe table", along with other options
OL,9,Fsuch as curfews or limits on addictive
OL,10,Ffeatures.
OL,12,FBut ministers appear to be leaning
OL,13,Ftowards a ban, with 90% of parents who
OL,14,Fresponded to the consultation saying
OL,15,Fthey would back one.
OL,17,FA government consultation on the
OL,18,Fissue, which closed on May 26,
OL,19,Freceived around 120,000 responses,
OL,20,Fmaking it the second-largest in
OL,21,Fhistory.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
