CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781475073
OL,3,CFunding boost for after-school clubs
OL,4,Cahead of expected social media ban
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Philipson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Every child should be able to
OL,8,Fenjoy sport and the creative arts, not
OL,9,Fjust the lucky few.
OL,11,F"Whether it's performing on stage,
OL,12,Fplaying sport, exploring nature or
OL,13,Fgetting involved in their community,
OL,14,Fthese experiences build confidence,
OL,15,Fspark ambition and help young people
OL,16,Fdiscover what they are capable of.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781475073
OL,3,CFunding boost for after-school clubs
OL,4,Cahead of expected social media ban
OL,6,F"As the world around our children
OL,7,Fcontinues to move fast, investment is
OL,8,Fabout making sure the childhood
OL,9,Fexperiences we truly value can once
OL,10,Fagain be for every young person,
OL,11,Fwherever they live."
OL,13,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy said: "I
OL,14,Fhave always been clear that talent is
OL,15,Feverywhere, but opportunity is not.
OL,17,F"A child who loves the arts shouldn't
OL,18,Fhave to be born into the right
OL,19,Fpostcode to pursue it, because we
OL,20,Fbelieve that Every Child Can excel in
OL,21,Fthe creative arts.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@TO]uD@dOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781475073
OL,3,CFunding boost for after-school clubs
OL,4,Cahead of expected social media ban
OL,6,F"By investing in these life-changing
OL,7,Fopportunities, we are supporting their
OL,8,Ffutures and delivering a positive step
OL,9,Fforward to break down the barriers for
OL,10,Fchildren and young people to access
OL,11,Fcreative opportunities that could in
OL,12,Fturn open up doors for their long-term
OL,13,Fcareers."
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
