PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781475073
OL,3,CFunding boost for after-school clubs
OL,4,Cahead of expected social media ban
OL,6,FThe Association of School and College
OL,7,FLeaders, said members "welcome the
OL,8,Fintent" behind the government's plans,
OL,9,Fbut still have concerns.
OL,11,F"As with many other government
OL,12,Fannouncements, there are several
OL,13,Fquestion marks over the capacity of
OL,14,Fschools and colleges to deliver these
OL,15,Faspirations," the group's general
OL,16,Fsecretary Pepe Di'Iasio said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781475073
OL,3,CFunding boost for after-school clubs
OL,4,Cahead of expected social media ban
OL,6,F"Schools and colleges already strive
OL,7,Fto provide excellent enrichment
OL,8,Fopportunities to their students, but
OL,9,Fthey have to operate within extremely
OL,10,Fchallenging financial and staffing
OL,11,Fconstraints
OL,13,F"Those pressures will not disappear
OL,14,Fsimply because the Government
OL,15,Fannounces new policies. It has to
OL,16,Ffocus more on how to turn aspirations
OL,17,Finto realities, particularly in areas
OL,18,Fof high disadvantage where these
OL,19,Fopportunities are most needed."
